oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Mrs. William Patrick Cashel, Nashville, Tennessee, between 1932 and 1951
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A photographic portrait of Mrs. Willam Patrick Cashel (Katie, nee Moran). She married William Patrick Cashel in Nashville, Tennessee on September 29th, 1897. Mrs. Cashel was a buyer in the Men’s Department for Castner Knott Company in the 1930s and early 1940s. Forms part of the John Lawrence Connelly Collection, 1 b & w photograph
